& [SLMWobbleFactorAttributionContract] is the contract for local wobble explanations
  + [contract_uuid] is 4e973948-5c67-4a16-a387-3a8c523226c3
  + [slice_id] is SLM-45
  + [depends_on] is SLM_Wobble_Contradiction_Contract, SLM_Evidence_Query_Surface_Contract, SLM_Primer_Provider_Evidence_Contract
  + [status] is verified_wsl

  & [AttributionPrinciple] is how wobble becomes diagnosable
    = must: preserve aggregate wobble score for routing
    = must: preserve dimension vector for diagnosis
    = must: emit local WobbleFactor records with stable ids
    = must: identify the local target kind and target ref when wobble has a local source
    = must: include human-readable local explanation in the primer
    - never: hide instability behind only the aggregate score

  & [FactorShape] is the v0 wobble factor record
    + [id] is parseable and stable within the measured wobble vector
    + [dimension] is the wobble dimension being raised
    + [target_kind] is token, span, relation, meaning, contradiction, deliberation, provider, workspace, or evidence
    + [target_ref] is the normalized local evidence ref
    + [score] is the factor contribution before dimension clamping
    + [explanation] is the local reason

  & [RuntimeProjection] is the Rust source surface
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/wobble.rs WobbleFactor id and target_kind
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/wobble.rs push_factor
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/primer.rs WobbleFactorPrimer
    + [proof_route] is WSL cargo test plus demo wobble factor inspection

  ! [Slice45SourceComplete] is accepted
    @ [source_gate] passed python slm_project/tools/slm_source_gate_check.py
    @ [wsl_cargo_test] passed 12 tests through CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/home/pinky/slm_rust_target and linker=/home/pinky/bin/zigcc
    @ [self_check] passed slm_self_check
    @ [demo_proof] design/compiler primer emitted 9 local wobble factors across role_instability, sense_instability, and span_boundary_instability
